  <brief_title>Erector Spinae Plane Block Analgesia for Lumbar Spine Fusion Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Can Bilateral Erector Spinae Plane Block Minimize Perioprative Opioid Consumption and Provide Satisfactory Analgesia for Lumbar Spine Fusion Surgery? A Randomized Controlled Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
