    <is_fda_regulated_device>No</is_fda_regulated_device>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to investigate the effect of a bilateral ultrasound guided&#xD;
      erector spinae plane block on the pain scores and opoid utiliziation in fusion surgery of the&#xD;
      lumbar spine.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Not yet recruiting</overall_status>
